SimpleAV-SDL is the SDL binding of SimpleAV, with a futher simplified API.
It is released under WTFPL v2.

You could simply compile it with 'make'.
Call 'make install' under root to install.

To use SimpleAV-SDL in your own program, just include SimpleAV_SDL.h in your program,
and use "-lSimpleAV_SDL -lSimpleAV" when calling gcc.